Easy setup and configuration
functinoal, API, accessibiltiy testing
Built-in reporters, custom reports 
CI, CD , DOCKER
Parallel testing
Auto wait
Built-in assertions
Multi tabl & multi window
Frames, shadow dom
Test parameter
Emulate mobile devices
Faster 

